title: Duplicate contacts only in "Dialler" app / Android 10 / Pixel 3A
content:
My "Contacts" app is perfect - only one of each contact. 

But for some reason, when I open the Phone Dialler (stock Android), and hit "Contacts" from the lower menu, there is around 10-15 of each contact. 

Any ideas what's happening here? The majority of the duplicates are empty - only have the name and no number or other details.
